'''Aberru''' neɣ '''Ajṛad''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Locusta'') d [[aburɣas]] yeṭṭafaren [[tafesna (tasnudert)|tafesna]] n [[Tuserdefriwin|tserdefriwin]] dges ugar n 20,000 n [[talmest|telmas]] yettidiren deg yidgan yemgaraden deg umadal, Aberru iga d yiwet n telmast n [[abẓiẓ|yebẓaẓ]] ilan (yesɛan) [[aṭar (agman)|iṭarren]] udfiren (n deffir) ttallen-t i wenttag anda tezmer ad tentteg azal n 20 n tikkal n teɣzi n tfekka-ynes.

Aberru d aɣersiw ilan (isɛan) aṭas n icenga d ingiren (iɛdawen) am [[aylal|iylalen]] d [[aɣeṛda|iɣeṛdayen]] d [[azrem|izerman]] d [[izinzer|izunzar]] akken daɣen i llan kra n [[adrar|izdayen]] d iɣerfan i t-itetten am kra n iɣerfan n [[Asya]] d [[imaziɣen]] n [[Isusiyen|Sus]].

